ention）控制咩野進入到你既意識，你既planning and recollection activities就係思考。意識係好多個大腦既mental faculties（emotion/motivation and rewarding systems/planning/desire/perception/memory/executive control），全部整合成一個「perceived, planning, actions」既結果<br />\n<br />\n所以你話人死左有冇意識？</blockquote><br />\n睇你點定義意識<br />\n你點知&quot;肉體&quot;得一個<br />\n我地發緊夢唔得既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}